# Assignments

## Structure
- Central assignment **bank** (all lessons, stored in backend).
- Students only see assignments **they are assigned**.
- Assignments displayed in dashboard with:
  - Title
  - Description
  - Language
  - Level
  - Category

## Pop-Out View
- Assignment opens in **sidebar/pop-out** alongside Playground.
- Allows student to read while coding.

## API
- `GET /categories` → ["Intro to Python", "Roblox Lua Basics", ...]
- `GET /assignments?category=...`
  → `[ { id, title, level, language, desc, category } ]`

## GitHub Export
- Submit button pushes code to:
  `/cognito-assignments/<assignmentId>.<ext>`
- Export requires GitHub login.
